<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="brake-v">brake <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /breɪk/    美 /breɪk/  </p>
<p>vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>刹 (车)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The driver <strong>braked</strong> (the bus) <strong>sharply</strong> / <strong>hard</strong>.
(公共汽车)司机突然急刹车。</p></div></div>